Package: cbamm
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive bayesian and advanced meta-analysis methods
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("CBAMM", "Developer", email = "cbamm.dev@example.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Implements advanced meta-analysis methods including network 
    meta-analysis, Bayesian approaches, and comprehensive sensitivity analyses.
    Provides transportability weighting for external validity, publication bias
    correction through PET-PEESE and selection models, robust variance estimation,
    and automated methodological guidance. Features intelligent method selection,
    multiple performance modes, and extensive utility functions for effect size
    conversion and statistical formatting.
